There are various ways to contribute to Gentoo, even without (much) technical knowledge.

== Community ==
* Help others by trying to answer questions on the forums
* Or on our IRC channels
* Improve existing documentation in our wiki
* Start a new article on our wiki

== Bugs ==
* Report bugs
* Try to confirm open bugs by reproducing them
* Try to offer solutions for open bugs

== Package maintenance ==
* Report version bumps
* Submit ebuilds for new packages
* Proxy-maintain an abandoned package
* Become a developer

